node.text:
I was so excited filming this I could barely get the words out! 😫 @covey 

First Of All Cleanser: 
Cleanser is so underrated, but it actually sets the mood for your whole routine. Covey's cleanser removes every stitch of makeup (yes, including waterproof mascara!), pollution and sweat. I roadtested dozens of cleanser formulas - and I knew we had found 'the one' when I could take off a full shoot day's makeup in less than 60 seconds without feeling dry or tight

Next Up Vitamin C Serum: 
We worked with @russakderm on all of our formulas, which is why our vitamin C serum is unlike any you've seen before. Next Up has 15% THD ascorbate, is fragrance-free (no hot dog water here), ultra-stable, ultra-gentle and multitasks for day and night to protect and repair skin

Last But Not Least Moisturizer:
Last, but definitely not least is our cloud-like moisturizer that's the perfect balance of hydrating and moisturizing. It's perfect during the day under makeup or as an overnight moisturizer to protect and nourish your skin barrier 

You can shop the full routine right here or on IG  to pre-order or click the link in my bio!!! 🥰

node.text: When I first started creating video content, I found talking to camera so challenging because it just felt super awkward. After some trial and error, I've picked up a few tricks that have helped me feel natural, authentic and comfortable talking on camera so now I'm basically a pro at talking to myself. 😂

node.title: How to talk to the camera like a pro and not feel like a weirdo

node.text: There’s no avoiding the short format vertical videos that sometimes incorporate  dancing. 😂 Sharing a few tips and tricks that I use to create all of IG Reels and TikToks. Are you team Reels Or TikTok or neither?!

node.title: Tips & tricks for creating Tiktok’s and IG Reels
